    "CaiTI's performance to assign Score to the Segments of the user responses. 7.",
    "22R-V Reasoner, R-V Guide, and R-V ValidatorDuring the 2,013 reflection-validation (R-V) process, R-V Reasoner and R-V Guide were activated 2,120 and 107 times, respectively.",
